latestPosts.caption:
Two founders. Two truths. One big fat lie! 😉

We played Two Truths and a Lie but turns out, you’ve been fed a few lies too... over the years. 👀
Watch till the end to find out which so called “truth” needs to be cancelled… and what to switch to instead 🦷💊
.
.

Our Beautywise story made waves in the Tank 🦈 .. turning dreams into a nationally recognised brand 😍
Hers’s a quick glimpse all that happened…

Sharing the Beautywise story on Shark Tank was surreal. 
What started as a personal mission is now a brand backed by science and loved by thousands ✨

Grateful, humbled, and just getting started. 
#BeautywiseOnSharkTank #FounderJourney #SkinHairScience #sharktankindiasonyliv #sharktankindia

Wrapping Up FY24-25! 💫
Looking back, we’re so grateful of how Beautywise has grown and evolved in every way, becoming a brand so many of you trust and love. From unforgettable milestones to the amazing community we’ve built together, this year has been nothing short of special.

Thank you for being part of our story ❤️ Here’s to another year of growth, innovation & making Beautywise even bigger! 🚀 
FY25-26 ✨
#Beautywise #WhatAYear #OnwardsAndUpwards #BeautyAndWellness

latestPosts.caption: Big moments call for big celebrations! Watch us relive the thrill of our Shark Tank journey with our amazing team, friends, and family. From nerves to cheers—this night had it all! Who else is tuning in? #SharkTankIndia #SonyLiv #BeautywiseOnSharkTank #Screening #screeningparty

From the initial spark of inspiration to seeing our products come to life and being embraced by all of you, every moment has been nothing short of magical ✨ 
I am deeply grateful to announce that Beautywise has successfully closed its first round of seed funding♥️ Thank you for your unwavering support as we embark on this exciting chapter of growth 🚀 
So grateful to our investors 🙏🏼 - AC Ventures, Fluid Ventures, Real Time Angel Fund, GSF, and Lets Venture Angel Fund… for not only believing in our mission but also for being integral parts of our journey. 
A special thanks to ACG Capsules .. to come on board as our investor and strategic partner 💫
Your support empowers us to keep introducing innovative products that
 redefine beauty and wellness ❤️

Beautywise, a startup in the dermatological and beauty supplement sector, proudly announces the successful completion of its first funding round, securing a substantial INR 6.5 Crores. With products available in over 500 pharmacies and endorsed by more than 150 Skin Clinics across India, Beautywise has demonstrated remarkable market success.
